# Mission Control Install Demo
# Run from repo root: vhs tapes/install.tape

Output images/install-demo.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1400
Set Height 900
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Shell "zsh"

Type "git clone https://github.com/Cyvid7-Darus10/claude-mission-control.git"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "cd claude-mission-control"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "./start.sh"
Enter
Sleep 15s
